SHE DIDN'T BELONG HERE.

00:46:24.700 --> 00:46:28.040 align:middle line:84%
THEN SHE GOT ANGRY,
FRUSTRATED,

00:46:28.040 --> 00:46:30.040 align:middle line:84%
AND TOOK IT OUT
ON THE BOYS.

00:46:30.040 --> 00:46:31.870 align:middle line:90%
BRAD MAINLY.

00:46:31.870 --> 00:46:33.290 align:middle line:90%
[CHUCKLES MIRTHLESSLY]

