01:02:43.680 --> 01:02:46.680 align:middle line:84%
[AMY WHISPERING]
STOP... STOP.

01:02:46.680 --> 01:02:48.220 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER AND JEERING]

01:02:48.220 --> 01:02:49.810 align:middle line:90%
LET'S GO.

01:02:54.850 --> 01:02:56.810 align:middle line:90%
[BOYS LAUGHING]

01:03:18.170 --> 01:03:19.840 align:middle line:90%
HEY.

01:03:19.840 --> 01:03:22.670 align:middle line:90%
HEY, HOW WAS PRACTICE?

01:03:23.050 --> 01:03:26.180 align:middle line:90%
ON THE RIGHT.

01:03:26.180 --> 01:03:27.600 align:middle line:90%
ARE YOU EXCITED?

01:03:27.600 --> 01:03:30.060 align:middle line:84%
BIG RACE COMING UP
IN A COUPLE OF DAYS.

01:03:30.060 --> 01:03:31.600 align:middle line:90%
YOU OKAY, PAL?

01:03:31.600 --> 01:03:34.690 align:middle line:84%
I'M JUST TIRED.
EVERYTHING'S FINE.

01:03:58.130 --> 01:04:00.090 align:middle line:90%
HEY, BRO!

01:04:00.090 --> 01:04:01.750 align:middle line:90%
WHERE YOU GOING?

01:04:01.750 --> 01:04:02.550 align:middle line:90%
CHESS CLUB, THEN TO CHURCH.

01:04:02.550 --> 01:04:05.050 align:middle line:84%
NO, SERIOUSLY,
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

01:04:05.050 --> 01:04:08.090 align:middle line:84%
YEAH, IT'S NONE
OF YOUR BUSINESS, BRO.

01:04:08.090 --> 01:04:09.220 align:middle line:90%
HEY...

01:04:09.220 --> 01:04:11.180 align:middle line:90%
YOU'RE NOT GOING, OKAY?

01:04:11.180 --> 01:04:12.640 align:middle line:84%
THE BERNARDS ARE JUST
LOOKING FOR A SUCKER.

01:04:12.640 --> 01:04:13.850 align:middle line:84%
THEY'RE NOT YOUR FRIEND,
TAKE IT FROM ME.

01:04:13.850 --> 01:04:15.140 align:middle line:84%
THEY JUST WANT TO
GET YOU IN TROUBLE.

01:04:15.140 --> 01:04:15.810 align:middle line:90%
TROUBLE?

01:04:15.810 --> 01:04:18.810 align:middle line:90%
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT TROUBLE?

01:04:18.810 --> 01:04:20.020 align:middle line:84%
I'VE NEVER BEEN BROUGHT HOME
BY THE POLICE,

01:04:20.020 --> 01:04:21.110 align:middle line:90%
NEVER BEEN TO COURT, OR JAIL.

01:04:21.110 --> 01:04:22.190 align:middle line:90%
THAT'S YOU, MAN.

01:04:22.190 --> 01:04:22.779 align:middle line:90%
AND THAT'S WHY--

01:04:22.779 --> 01:04:26.360 align:middle line:90%
THAT'S WHY MOM'S NOT HERE!

01:04:26.360 --> 01:04:28.360 align:middle line:84%
BECAUSE YOU WERE
SO MUCH TROUBLE.

01:04:31.410 --> 01:04:33.740 align:middle line:90%
[PRANK VIDEO PLAYING BACK]

01:04:33.740 --> 01:04:36.160 align:middle line:84%
OKAY, VERY FUNNY,
WE ALL LAUGHED.

01:04:36.160 --> 01:04:37.960 align:middle line:90%
NOW STOP, OKAY?

01:04:37.960 --> 01:04:39.250 align:middle line:90%
[BANGING AND LAUGHTER IN VIDEO]

01:04:39.250 --> 01:04:40.750 align:middle line:84%
COME ON, MAN,
YOU'RE MESSING WITH ME.

01:04:40.750 --> 01:04:42.380 align:middle line:84%
NOT EVEN YOU WOULD DO
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

01:04:42.380 --> 01:04:44.210 align:middle line:84%
[TYSON]:
OH, YEAH?

01:04:44.210 --> 01:04:46.130 align:middle line:90%
JUST ASK AMY.

01:04:46.130 --> 01:04:49.140 align:middle line:84%
THIS BURN IS GONNA
BE LEGENDARY.

01:05:04.230 --> 01:05:05.190 align:middle line:90%
BRAD!

01:05:05.190 --> 01:05:07.950 align:middle line:90%
BRAD...

01:05:07.950 --> 01:05:09.029 align:middle line:90%
JULIE?

01:05:09.029 --> 01:05:10.029 align:middle line:90%
IT'S TYSON,

01:05:10.029 --> 01:05:12.370 align:middle line:84%
YOU HAVE TO
DO SOMETHING.

01:05:12.370 --> 01:05:13.029 align:middle line:84%
TYSON IS NONE
OF MY BUSINESS.

01:05:13.029 --> 01:05:15.870 align:middle line:90%
IS ALEX?

01:05:22.340 --> 01:05:24.170 align:middle line:90%
TYSON!

01:05:24.170 --> 01:05:26.210 align:middle line:90%
WHAT DO YOU WANT, COLEMAN?

01:05:26.210 --> 01:05:27.590 align:middle line:90%
DO YOU WANT TO PLAY?

01:05:27.590 --> 01:05:29.840 align:middle line:84%
I GOTTA WARN YOU, THOUGH, MAN,
WE DON'T PLAY REZ RULES HERE.

01:05:29.840 --> 01:05:30.180 align:middle line:90%
GIVE ME THE PHONE.

01:05:30.180 --> 01:05:32.090 align:middle line:90%
WHAT PHONE?

01:05:32.090 --> 01:05:34.310 align:middle line:84%
THE PHONE WITH THE VIDEO!
GIVE IT TO ME!

01:05:34.310 --> 01:05:38.520 align:middle line:90%
OH, THAT PHONE.

01:05:38.520 --> 01:05:42.190 align:middle line:84%
NO, I DON'T THINK YOU ASKED ME
NICE ENOUGH.

01:05:46.440 --> 01:05:48.490 align:middle line:84%
I'M ONLY GOING TO
ASK YOU THIS ONCE.

01:05:48.490 --> 01:05:50.990 align:middle line:84%
GIVE ME THE PHONE,
OR I PROMISE YOU,

01:05:50.990 --> 01:05:52.320 align:middle line:90%
YOU'RE GOING TO REGRET IT.

01:05:52.320 --> 01:05:53.570 align:middle line:90%
YOU UNDERSTAND?

01:05:53.570 --> 01:05:55.200 align:middle line:90%
YOU WANT IT?

01:05:55.200 --> 01:05:57.620 align:middle line:90%
COME GET IT.

01:05:59.500 --> 01:06:01.420 align:middle line:90%
WELL?

01:06:01.420 --> 01:06:04.090 align:middle line:90%
COME ON, COLEMAN,

01:06:04.090 --> 01:06:05.210 align:middle line:90%
BRING IT ON.

01:06:16.390 --> 01:06:19.020 align:middle line:90%
TOLD YOU HE WAS CHICKEN.

01:06:21.140 --> 01:06:22.020 align:middle line:90%
LET'S GO, GAME ON!

01:06:30.360 --> 01:06:32.279 align:middle line:84%
FINALLY SHOWING UP
FOR THAT DETENTION

01:06:32.279 --> 01:06:33.450 align:middle line:90%
FROM THREE MONTHS AGO?

01:06:33.450 --> 01:06:35.870 align:middle line:84%
LOOK, I WANT TO
TELL YOU SOMETHING,

01:06:35.870 --> 01:06:36.410 align:middle line:84%
BUT FIRST, I WANT TO KNOW
IF YOU WILL LISTEN TO ME.

01:06:36.410 --> 01:06:39.410 align:middle line:90%
I'M LISTENING, BRAD.

01:06:39.410 --> 01:06:41.040 align:middle line:90%
TYSON.

01:06:41.040 --> 01:06:42.500 align:middle line:90%
COME WITH ME.

01:06:42.500 --> 01:06:44.880 align:middle line:90%
NOW, TYSON!

01:06:46.340 --> 01:06:48.960 align:middle line:90%
GIVE IT TO ME,

01:06:48.960 --> 01:06:49.590 align:middle line:90%
THE PHONE.

01:06:49.590 --> 01:06:51.970 align:middle line:90%
GIVE ME THE PHONE.

01:06:52.430 --> 01:06:54.510 align:middle line:90%
YOU'RE DONE, TYSON.

01:06:54.510 --> 01:06:56.050 align:middle line:84%
IT WAS JUST--
IT WAS JUST A PRANK.

01:06:56.050 --> 01:06:57.600 align:middle line:90%
IT WAS, LIKE, A TEAM THING.

01:06:57.600 --> 01:06:58.260 align:middle line:84%
I DIDN'T UPLOAD IT
ON YOUTUBE OR ANYTHING--

01:06:58.260 --> 01:06:59.770 align:middle line:84%
YEAH, YOU
BETTER NOT HAVE,

01:06:59.770 --> 01:07:02.310 align:middle line:84%
BECAUSE THAT IS
A VERY SERIOUS LEGAL MATTER.

01:07:02.310 --> 01:07:03.100 align:middle line:90%
THAT WAS NO PRANK.

01:07:03.100 --> 01:07:05.860 align:middle line:84%
WHAT YOU DID
WAS CRUEL AND UNUSUAL,

01:07:05.860 --> 01:07:08.270 align:middle line:84%
AND I WOULD LOVE TO SAY
MORE TO YOU,

01:07:08.270 --> 01:07:09.820 align:middle line:90%
BUT I ALSO LIKE MY JOB.

01:07:09.820 --> 01:07:12.610 align:middle line:84%
YOU KNOW NOTHING
ABOUT BEING ON A TEAM.

01:07:12.610 --> 01:07:14.610 align:middle line:84%
THAT STUNT HAS GOT YOU
OFF THIS TEAM,

01:07:14.610 --> 01:07:17.120 align:middle line:84%
AND, WHEN I'M DONE WITH YOU,
SUSPENDED FROM SCHOOL.

01:07:19.240 --> 01:07:20.240 align:middle line:90%
NO, NO, LISTEN, MISS,

01:07:20.240 --> 01:07:22.290 align:middle line:84%
YOU'RE NOT GOING TO
WIN ANYTHING WITHOUT ME.

01:07:22.290 --> 01:07:23.370 align:middle line:90%
YOU NEED ME.

01:07:24.620 --> 01:07:28.420 align:middle line:84%
MY JOB HERE
ISN'T TO WIN TROPHIES, TYSON.

01:07:34.220 --> 01:07:37.140 align:middle line:84%
SO YOU GUYS
TOOK CARE OF IT ALL, HUH?

01:07:37.140 --> 01:07:37.800 align:middle line:84%
THAT'S GREAT,
THAT'S JUST GREAT.

01:07:37.800 --> 01:07:40.100 align:middle line:84%
ALEX, WHAT'S
WRONG WITH YOU?

01:07:40.100 --> 01:07:41.100 align:middle line:90%
BRAD--

01:07:41.100 --> 01:07:41.770 align:middle line:90%
DON'T YOU GET IT?

01:07:41.770 --> 01:07:43.680 align:middle line:90%
EVERYONE'S LOOKING OUT FOR ME,

01:07:43.680 --> 01:07:45.100 align:middle line:84%
LIKE THE LITTLE BLIND KID
NEEDS TO BE HELPED

01:07:45.100 --> 01:07:45.810 align:middle line:90%
FROM BEING ABUSED OR SOMETHING.

01:07:45.810 --> 01:07:47.650 align:middle line:84%
YEAH, BUT YOU WERE
BEING ABUSED.

01:07:47.650 --> 01:07:50.480 align:middle line:90%
THAT IS NOT THE POINT, BRAD.

01:07:50.480 --> 01:07:51.980 align:middle line:90%
SURE, I WAS HUMILIATED,

01:07:51.980 --> 01:07:54.650 align:middle line:84%
BUT MY SKIN
IS THICKER THAN THAT.

01:07:56.610 --> 01:07:59.950 align:middle line:84%
DON'T YOU GUYS THINK FOR ONCE
I MIGHT HAVE MY OWN AGENDA?

01:08:00.490 --> 01:08:04.080 align:middle line:90%
ALL RIGHT, ALEX,

01:08:04.080 --> 01:08:05.210 align:middle line:84%
WHAT DO YOU
WANT TO DO, MAN?

01:08:10.380 --> 01:08:13.130 align:middle line:90%
COACH?

01:08:13.130 --> 01:08:14.920 align:middle line:90%
ALEX.

01:08:14.920 --> 01:08:18.140 align:middle line:84%
DON'T WORRY,
I'M TAKING CARE OF IT.

01:08:18.140 --> 01:08:20.430 align:middle line:84%
YOU'RE CUTTING TYSON
FROM THE TEAM, AREN'T YOU?

01:08:20.430 --> 01:08:22.260 align:middle line:84%
EVERYTHING'S
GOING TO BE OKAY.

01:08:22.260 --> 01:08:23.180 align:middle line:90%
DON'T CUT HIM.

01:08:23.180 --> 01:08:24.520 align:middle line:90%
ALEX--

01:08:24.520 --> 01:08:25.520 align:middle line:90%
LET HIM RACE.

01:08:25.520 --> 01:08:26.520 align:middle line:90%
WHAT?

01:08:26.520 --> 01:08:28.149 align:middle line:84%
LET HIM RACE
TOMORROW, PLEASE?

01:08:29.689 --> 01:08:31.189 align:middle line:84%
LOOK, IF TYSON
CAN'T RUN TOMORROW, THEN HE...

01:08:31.189 --> 01:08:33.149 align:middle line:84%
HE CAN GO AROUND SCHOOL,
TO EVERYONE, BRAGGING

01:08:33.149 --> 01:08:36.029 align:middle line:84%
THAT THE BLIND KID HAD TO HIDE
BEHIND TEACHERS

01:08:36.029 --> 01:08:39.529 align:middle line:90%
AND BRAD COLEMAN TO BEAT HIM.

01:08:39.529 --> 01:08:42.700 align:middle line:84%
HE MADE THAT VIDEO
BECAUSE I THREATEN HIM.

01:08:42.700 --> 01:08:44.660 align:middle line:90%
HE KNOWS THAT I CAN BEAT HIM.

01:08:44.660 --> 01:08:46.330 align:middle line:90%
ALL I WANT,

01:08:46.330 --> 01:08:46.100 align:middle line:90%
ALL I AM ASKING FROM YOU,

01:08:46.100 --> 01:08:48.790 align:middle line:90%
IS A CHANCE TO ACTUALLY DO IT.

01:08:51.210 --> 01:08:53.380 align:middle line:90%
[SIGHS]

01:08:53.380 --> 01:08:55.210 align:middle line:84%
NORMALLY, ALEX,
I WOULD SAY NO WAY.

01:08:55.210 --> 01:08:58.800 align:middle line:84%
NORMALLY, I WOULD TELL YOU
THAT WHAT HE DID WAS AWFUL,

01:08:58.800 --> 01:09:03.260 align:middle line:84%
AND THAT HE DESERVES
TO BE PUNISHED.

01:09:03.260 --> 01:09:05.100 align:middle line:90%
NORMALLY.

01:09:08.229 --> 01:09:09.229 align:middle line:90%


01:09:11.690 --> 01:09:13.729 align:middle line:84%
HEY, UH, CAN I
ASK YOU A QUESTION?

01:09:13.729 --> 01:09:16.569 align:middle line:84%
YEAH, SURE, AS LONG
AS I CAN ASK YOU ONE.

01:09:16.569 --> 01:09:18.279 align:middle line:90%
ALL RIGHT.

01:09:18.279 --> 01:09:19.569 align:middle line:90%
HOW DID YOU GO BLIND?

01:09:19.569 --> 01:09:20.279 align:middle line:90%
I GOT REALLY SICK

01:09:20.279 --> 01:09:22.529 align:middle line:84%
WHEN I WAS ABOUT
TWO YEARS OLD.

01:09:22.529 --> 01:09:23.580 align:middle line:90%
SOME KIND OF INFECTION.

01:09:23.580 --> 01:09:25.740 align:middle line:90%
I GOT A REALLY HIGH FEVER,

01:09:25.740 --> 01:09:27.410 align:middle line:84%
AND IT ENDED UP SWELLING
MY OPTIC NERVE,

01:09:27.410 --> 01:09:30.170 align:middle line:90%
AND I WAS BLIND.

01:09:30.170 --> 01:09:33.500 align:middle line:84%
DO YOU, LIKE,
REMEMBER SEEING?

01:09:33.500 --> 01:09:35.050 align:middle line:90%
NOT REALLY, NO.

01:09:35.050 --> 01:09:36.550 align:middle line:84%
I MEAN, I CAN'T
REALLY DESCRIBE

01:09:36.550 --> 01:09:38.380 align:middle line:84%
WHAT SOMETHING LOOKS LIKE
TO YOU NOW,

01:09:38.380 --> 01:09:40.680 align:middle line:90%
BUT I DREAM, YOU KNOW?

01:09:40.680 --> 01:09:41.720 align:middle line:90%
IT'S MY MOM...

01:09:41.720 --> 01:09:47.140 align:middle line:84%
SHE... SHE SEEMS TO THINK
THAT IT WAS HER FAULT.

01:09:47.140 --> 01:09:48.430 align:middle line:90%
THAT'S HARSH.

01:09:48.430 --> 01:09:50.600 align:middle line:84%
NO WONDER SHE'S
ALL OVER YOU AND STUFF.

01:09:50.600 --> 01:09:52.309 align:middle line:84%
YEAH, I MEAN, WE BOTH TRY
TO HELP HER OUT WITH IT,

01:09:52.309 --> 01:09:55.690 align:middle line:90%
BUT IT'S STILL THERE.

01:09:55.690 --> 01:09:58.440 align:middle line:84%
MY DAD WANTS ME
TO BE INDEPENDENT,

01:09:58.440 --> 01:10:00.240 align:middle line:90%
SHE WANTS TO HANGS ON.

01:10:01.360 --> 01:10:02.030 align:middle line:90%
WELL, UH,

01:10:02.030 --> 01:10:06.120 align:middle line:84%
IF YOU WANT
MY ADVICE, JUST...

01:10:06.120 --> 01:10:08.250 align:middle line:90%
LET HER HANG ON.

01:10:12.420 --> 01:10:14.210 align:middle line:84%
ALL RIGHT,
WE'RE GOING UP A HILL,

01:10:14.210 --> 01:10:16.130 align:middle line:90%
AND STAY TO THE RIGHT.

01:10:16.130 --> 01:10:17.380 align:middle line:90%
GOT IT.

01:10:20.800 --> 01:10:23.510 align:middle line:90%
NOW IT'S MY TURN.

01:10:23.510 --> 01:10:26.470 align:middle line:84%
THAT FIRST DAY AT PRACTICE,
AGAINST TYSON,

01:10:26.470 --> 01:10:27.470 align:middle line:90%
WHY DID YOU SLOW DOWN?

01:10:27.470 --> 01:10:28.850 align:middle line:84%
I MEAN,
WHY COULDN'T WE--

01:10:28.850 --> 01:10:32.980 align:middle line:84%
WHY COULDN'T WE
PASS HIM?

01:10:32.980 --> 01:10:34.650 align:middle line:84%
I KIND OF GUESSED
YOU WERE GOING TO ASK THAT.

01:10:34.650 --> 01:10:36.610 align:middle line:90%
YEAH, I MEAN,

01:10:36.610 --> 01:10:39.650 align:middle line:84%
YOU'LL PROBABLY LAUGH,
BUT, UH...

01:10:39.650 --> 01:10:41.320 align:middle line:90%
THOSE GUYS ARE REAL ATHLETES.

01:10:41.320 --> 01:10:44.990 align:middle line:84%
YOU KNOW, I THOUGHT THAT
MAYBE I DIDN'T DESERVE TO WIN.

01:10:44.990 --> 01:10:48.660 align:middle line:84%
LIKE, MAYBE
I WASN'T GOOD ENOUGH.

01:10:48.660 --> 01:10:51.660 align:middle line:90%
I KNOW IT'S STUPID, BUT...

01:10:51.660 --> 01:10:54.920 align:middle line:90%
I DON'T KNOW, I...

01:10:54.920 --> 01:10:56.710 align:middle line:84%
I THOUGHT THAT IF WE DIDN'T
DRAW ATTENTION TO OURSELVES,

01:10:56.710 --> 01:11:01.260 align:middle line:84%
THAT THE TEAM
WOULD ACCEPT US.

01:11:01.260 --> 01:11:03.840 align:middle line:90%
WE'RE OUR OWN TEAM.

01:11:03.840 --> 01:11:05.640 align:middle line:90%


01:11:20.110 --> 01:11:22.150 align:middle line:90%
[ALL LAUGHING AND CHATTING]

01:11:22.150 --> 01:11:23.700 align:middle line:84%
SOMEBODY FOUND
THE BATHROOM, HUH?

01:11:23.700 --> 01:11:25.110 align:middle line:84%
WELL, IF YOUR PLANTS
DON'T DIE

01:11:25.110 --> 01:11:26.570 align:middle line:84%
IN THE NEXT
COUPLE OF DAYS,

01:11:26.570 --> 01:11:27.370 align:middle line:90%
THEN, YEAH, I FOUND IT.

01:11:27.370 --> 01:11:29.790 align:middle line:84%
WELL SAID.
ABSOLUTELY DISGUSTING.

01:11:29.790 --> 01:11:31.370 align:middle line:84%
I'D LIKE TO RAISE
A TOAST, PLEASE,

01:11:31.370 --> 01:11:32.580 align:middle line:90%
TO OUR TWO CHAMPIONS.

01:11:32.580 --> 01:11:34.040 align:middle line:90%
HEAR, HEAR!

01:11:34.040 --> 01:11:36.170 align:middle line:84%
[CLINKING GLASSES]
THERE YOU GO.

01:11:40.630 --> 01:11:41.670 align:middle line:90%
MOM?

01:11:41.670 --> 01:11:43.760 align:middle line:90%
OH. GOT IT.

01:11:43.760 --> 01:11:46.550 align:middle line:84%
I THINK THESE TWO GUYS
ARE GOING TO KICK BUTT TOMORROW,

01:11:46.550 --> 01:11:47.050 align:middle line:90%
WHAT DO YOU THINK, JULIE?

01:11:47.050 --> 01:11:48.720 align:middle line:90%
I THINK JULIE KNOWS

01:11:48.720 --> 01:11:50.220 align:middle line:90%
ALL ABOUT BUTTS, DOESN'T SHE?

01:11:50.220 --> 01:11:52.220 align:middle line:84%
HOW ABOUT
MY FORK IN YOURS?

01:11:54.270 --> 01:11:55.480 align:middle line:90%
[BRAD]: THESE AGAIN?

01:11:55.480 --> 01:11:57.809 align:middle line:84%
YOU'RE, LIKE, THE MOST STUBBORN
LITTLE GUY I'VE EVER MET,

01:11:57.809 --> 01:11:58.730 align:middle line:90%
YOU KNOW THAT?

01:11:58.730 --> 01:12:02.320 align:middle line:84%
I KNOW, BUT, BRAD,
YOU DESERVE THESE, OKAY?

01:12:02.320 --> 01:12:03.400 align:middle line:90%
PLEASE, JUST TAKE THEM.

01:12:03.400 --> 01:12:05.570 align:middle line:84%
PLEASE,
JUST TAKE THEM.

01:12:05.570 --> 01:12:08.570 align:middle line:90%
[CLAPS] HEY.

01:12:08.570 --> 01:12:09.700 align:middle line:84%
I'M GOING GET US
SOME ICE CREAM. YUP.

01:12:09.700 --> 01:12:11.700 align:middle line:84%
HEY, UM, THANKS
FOR EVERYTHING, GUYS,

01:12:11.700 --> 01:12:12.750 align:middle line:90%
BUT I SHOULD GO.

01:12:12.750 --> 01:12:13.580 align:middle line:90%
ARE YOU SURE?

01:12:13.580 --> 01:12:14.910 align:middle line:84%
ALL RIGHT,
WE'LL SEE YOU TOMORROW.

01:12:14.910 --> 01:12:16.290 align:middle line:90%
STRETCH OUT.

01:12:16.290 --> 01:12:17.210 align:middle line:90%
THANKS, GUYS.

01:12:17.210 --> 01:12:18.250 align:middle line:84%
-BYE!
-SEE YOU, BRAD.

01:12:18.250 --> 01:12:18.960 align:middle line:90%
SEE YOU GUYS.

01:12:51.950 --> 01:12:52.790 align:middle line:90%
OH, YOU'RE BACK.

01:12:52.790 --> 01:12:54.790 align:middle line:90%
YEAH, YOU KNOW,

01:12:54.790 --> 01:12:56.290 align:middle line:84%
I THINK I'M GOING TO STAY
FOR SOME ICE CREAM.

01:12:56.290 --> 01:12:57.410 align:middle line:90%
GREAT.

01:12:57.410 --> 01:12:59.960 align:middle line:84%
AND BY THE WAY, BRAD,
THOSE REALLY AREN'T CHARITY.

01:12:59.960 --> 01:13:02.960 align:middle line:84%
OKAY, GOOD BECAUSE,
YOU KNOW, I--

01:13:02.960 --> 01:13:04.130 align:middle line:90%
WE KNOW.

01:13:04.130 --> 01:13:06.010 align:middle line:84%
